{"tid":21124,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果將lihkg既故事拍成電影","createTime":"2016-12-03T16:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T17:03:55.000Z","uid":36134,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a56cb04929d7b40fe5f7e0e709203a24f7e008ed","tid":21124,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"我相信一定好精彩<br />\n一段高智商高智謀既推翻早泄帝國既故事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果用陳某既風格去拍<br />\n成件事變得好高智謀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下內容純屬ff<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先 來一招公子獻code<br />\nPlus仔向連尼住獻上apps code<br />\n之後成班開發者向外發佈消息<br />\n話自己唔打算繼續或者唔表態<br />\n向外示弱 <br />\n令外界同情開發者<br />\n更令到早泄輕敵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後早泄再接受hk01訪問<br />\n串串貢 大失人心 <br />\n不戰而屈人之兵 <br />\n如果段訪問都係改成由有人策劃<br />\n更加精彩<br />\n輕敵之計 玩敵如撚狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且 呢段期間<br />\n一直暗渡陳倉<br />\n建立新壇 做好左<br />\n唔急住發佈<br />\n仲選定左hkg+末日<br />\n所有人絕望既一刻發佈<br />\n以救世者既姿態降臨<br />\n盡得人心  <br />\n完美無瑕既計劃<br />\n絲絲入扣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n㕷<br />\n天下已經在他們手中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗起都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有咩劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4c5544b8fa60fca4c3d2ce9ccb4485b0805a57","tid":21124,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"喬布斯"},{"pid":"5a2324f4702430fa5f7d1b154464dcc565b2830f","tid":21124,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:40:29.000Z","msg":"加埋一開波點俾高登打壓<br />\n早洩當佢地狗咁撚<br />\n再連之後嘅劇情<br />\n冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ca1bb29f7d75646504feb9cd75b93ff8ac111e","tid":21124,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"257ada30e36d03930997edf92b503dea1ae8274d","tid":21124,"uid":26097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"又正啵"}]}